785
01:08:15,760 --> 01:08:18,160
This woman you sing of.

786
01:08:21,660 --> 01:08:24,059
'Tis the lady of Luthien.

787
01:08:24,060 --> 01:08:29,260
The elf-maiden who gave her
love to Beren, a mortal.

788
01:08:31,260 --> 01:08:33,360
What happened to her?

789
01:08:35,661 --> 01:08:38,061
She died.

790
01:08:42,061 --> 01:08:44,361
Get some sleep, Frodo.

791
01:08:54,861 --> 01:08:58,761
The power of Isengard is at your command...

792
01:08:59,061 --> 01:09:03,262
