793
01:09:06,862 --> 01:09:12,462
Build me an army worthy of Mordor.

794
01:09:18,162 --> 01:09:22,462
What orders from Mordor, my lord?
What does the Eye command?

795
01:09:23,162 --> 01:09:24,962
We have work to do.

796
