Stay here.

803
01:11:13,967 --> 01:11:16,166
My tomato's burst.

804
01:11:16,167 --> 01:11:18,266
Could I have some bacon?

805
01:11:18,267 --> 01:11:20,367
Want a tomato, Sam?

806
01:11:20,767 --> 01:11:24,367
- What are you doing?!
- Tomatoes, sausages, nice crispy bacon.

807
01:11:24,667 --> 01:11:27,267
- We saved some for you, Mr. Frodo.
- Put it out, you fools!

808
01:11:27,567 --> 01:11:31,367
- Put it out!
- That's nice! Ash on my tomatoes!

809
01:11:39,968 --> 01:11:41,668
Go!

810
01:12:05,829 --> 01:12:09,829
{\an8} [Adûnaic] ♫ <i>Bârî'n Katha-râd</i> ♫
{\an8} [English] ♫ The Lords of the Eternal life ♫

