{\an8} [Adûnaic] ♫ <i>Nêbâ-bîtham Ma-gâna-nanê</i> ♫
{\an8} [English] ♫ We renounce our Creator ♫

815
01:12:35,270 --> 01:12:36,670
Back, you devils!

816
01:12:39,830 --> 01:12:44,830
{\an8} [Adûnaic] ♫ <i>Nêtab~ Dâur~</i> ♫
{\an8} [English] ♫ We cling to the darkness ♫

