[Black Speech] <i>...ashi...</i>
[English] ...only...

819
01:13:11,331 --> 01:13:13,331
[Black Speech] <i>...gurum!</i>
[English] ...death!

820
01:14:00,173 --> 01:14:01,373
Frodo!

821
01:14:06,073 --> 01:14:07,273
Oh, Sam.

822
01:14:44,375 --> 01:14:45,375
Strider!

823
01:14:48,075 --> 01:14:53,375
- Help him, Strider.
- He's been stabbed by a Morgul blade.

824
01:14:55,075 --> 01:14:59,775
This is beyond my skill to heal.
He needs elvish medicine.

825
01:15:04,576 --> 01:15:05,576
Hurry!

826
01:15:05,876 --> 01:15:09,676
We're six days from Rivendell!
He'll never make it!

827
01:15:09,976 --> 01:15:11,776
Hold on, Frodo.

828
01:15:12,376 --> 01:15:14,376
Gandalf!

829
01:15:50,837 --> 01:16:00,837
{\an8} [Quenya] ♫ <i> I Cemen Nurrua ... </i> ♫
{\an8} [English] ♫ The earth groans ... ♫

