Look, Frodo. It's Mr. Bilbo's trolls.

835
01:17:57,782 --> 01:18:00,483
Mr. Frodo? He's going cold.

836
01:18:03,483 --> 01:18:05,183
Is he going to die?

837
01:18:05,483 --> 01:18:10,183
He's passing into the shadow world.
He'll soon become a wraith like them.

838
01:18:15,483 --> 01:18:19,183
- They're close.
- Sam, do you know the Athelas plant?

839
01:18:19,583 --> 01:18:20,982
- Athelas?
- Kingsfoil.

840
01:18:20,983 --> 01:18:22,183
Kingsfoil, aye, it's a weed.

841
01:18:22,483 --> 01:18:25,484
It may help to slow the poisoning.
Hurry!

842
01:18:39,984 --> 01:18:43,984
What's this, a ranger caught off his guard?

843
01:18:47,844 --> 01:19:09,084
{\an8} [Sindarin] ♫ <i> Tinuviel elvanui ... </i> ♫
{\an8} [English] ♫ Tinuviel the elven-fair ... ♫

844
01:19:09,085 --> 01:19:10,385
Frodo.

845
01:19:11,346 --> 01:19:11,534
{\an8} [Sindarin] ♫ <i> ... elleth alfirin. </i> ♫
{\an8} [English] ♫ ... immortal maiden. ♫

846
01:19:11,535 --> 01:19:15,935
[Sindarin] <i>Im Arwen, Telin le thaed.</i>
[English] I Arwen, I come to help you.

847
